{"tid":1027255,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"佢個頭係點剪㗎？","createTime":"2019-02-18T16:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T07:48:55.000Z","uid":55133,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dda871d235b88c3465b8fe4c44eb40b476e21521","tid":1027255,"uid":55133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:50:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/95KbDetLczQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F95KbDetLczQ&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEsjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=018c2724\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/95KbDetLczQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">妥瑞氏症的症狀包含聲音型和運動型抽動綜合症，會不受自主控制地發出清喉嚨的聲音或聳肩、搖頭晃腦等。患者本身並非故意或習慣性做出這些動作</span>，其症狀乃肇因於腦內多巴胺不平衡。治療方式一般採取抗精神病藥抑制症狀，或行為治療等。症狀通常時好時壞，與患者所處環境造成的心理壓力有一定的相關性，家庭、學校與社會對此疾病的不認識或多或少會加深正常人與妥瑞症患者間的誤解，進而誘發更強烈的症狀。常見的誤解例如：把妥瑞氏症患者當成調皮搗蛋的壞習慣，進而要求患者以接受體罰等方式刻意矯正其抽動症狀<br />\n點解可以剪到咁齊嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a46e1238ab24d783a696ea408902eb5c9010d4","tid":1027255,"uid":55133,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:56:12.000Z","msg":"有無髮型師傅可以解答下"},{"pid":"c9ee039f0720e9d2bd8cb66e524e3c4992d1ef57","tid":1027255,"uid":235520,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T23:49:06.000Z","msg":"唔知你真膠定假膠<br />\n認真答左你先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5BSBjeX2W3o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5BSBjeX2W3o&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEsjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=80d7b5dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5BSBjeX2W3o</a><br />\n<br />\ntwo block haircut<br />\n直接拎D相比髮型師睇<br />\n同佢講想剪呢個韓仔頭<br />\n<br />\n重點係兩邊本身要留得厚 <br />\n類似UNDERCUT既概念"},{"pid":"62801d4a0cc9b567fe94db11a5dd27974b67008f","tid":1027255,"uid":84128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:04:26.000Z","msg":"我都好似有少少咁<br />\n好似強迫症咁 會迫自己做某樣野<br />\n但當有野集中左 唔留意佢個陣就無野"},{"pid":"35283fb32572e0eee